lead_paragraph: Germany's dismal record against Italy in major tournaments is not a source of trauma for the world champions, who will face their international nemesis in the Euro 2016 last eight, coach Joachim Loew said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: We Have No Trauma About Italy, Germany's Loew Says of Nemesis
